sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box "Hardware Domain" #f9f9f9
        participant Periph as Peripheral<br/>(Timer/UART)
        participant INTC as INTCPS<br/>(Controller)
        participant CPU as ARM Core
    end

    box "Software Domain" #e1f5fe
        participant Vector as Vector Table
        participant Entry as ASM Entry
        participant Core as Kernel Dispatcher
        participant ISR as Driver ISR
    end
    
    Note over Periph,ISR: ASYNCHRONOUS INTERRUPT FLOW (Steady Phase)
    
    Periph->>INTC: 1. Assert Signal (IRQ Line)
    
    Note over INTC: Priority Check & Arbitration
    
    INTC->>CPU: 2. Assert ARM IRQ Line
    
    Note right of CPU: Finish Current Instruction
    
    alt IRQ Masked (CPSR.I = 1)
        Note right of CPU: **PENDING:** CPU ignores request.<br/>Wait for unmask.
    else IRQ Enabled (CPSR.I = 0)
        activate CPU
        Note right of CPU: **HARDWARE ACTIONS:**<br/>1. Mode: SVC/USR -> IRQ<br/>2. LR_irq = PC + 4<br/>3. SPSR_irq = CPSR<br/>4. Mask IRQ (I=1)<br/>5. Jump VBAR + 0x18
        
        CPU->>Vector: 3. Jump to VBAR + 0x18
        deactivate CPU
        
        Note right of Vector: ldr pc, =vector_irq
        
        Vector->>Entry: Branch to Entry Stub
        activate Entry
        
        Note right of Entry: **CONTEXT SAVE:**<br/>1. sub lr, lr, #4 (Fix Return Addr)<br/>2. push {r0-r12, lr, spsr}<br/>3. Switch to IRQ Stack
        
        Entry->>Core: 4. irq_handler()
        activate Core
        
        Note right of Core: **DISPATCH:**<br/>1. Read INTC_SIR_IRQ<br/>2. Identify Source (0-127)
        
        Core->>ISR: 5. Call Specific ISR
        activate ISR
        
        Note right of ISR: **DRIVER LOGIC:**<br/>1. Read Status<br/>2. Clear Peripheral Flag<br/>3. Data Handling
        
        ISR-->>Core: return
        deactivate ISR
        
        Core->>INTC: 6. ACK (NewIRQAgree)
        INTC-->>CPU: De-assert IRQ Line
        
        Core-->>Entry: return
        deactivate Core
        
        Note right of Entry: **CONTEXT RESTORE:**<br/>1. pop {r0-r12, lr, spsr}
        
        Entry->>CPU: 7. Exception Return<br/>(subs pc, lr, #4)
        deactivate Entry
        
        activate CPU
        Note right of CPU: **HARDWARE RETURN:**<br/>1. Restore CPSR<br/>2. Mode IRQ -> SVC/USR<br/>3. I-bit cleared (Unmask)<br/>4. Resume Execution
        deactivate CPU
    end